            <h3 id="aboutname"> </h3>
            <h4>I grew up in <a href="http://wikitravel.org/en/Kolkata" target="_blank">Kolkata</a>, a lovely city on the eastern coast of India. I was lucky to have studied at one of the most famous schools in India, 
                <a href="http://southpoint.edu.in/" target="_blank">South Point</a>. <br><br> Currently, I am an undergraduate student at the 
                <a href="http://www.iitp.ac.in/" target="_blank">Indian Institute of Technology, Patna, </a> studying Computer Science and Engineering. <br><br>
                My most favourite city after my hometown is <a href="http://wikitravel.org/en/Delhi" target="_blank">Delhi</a>, since I spent my first summer alone here.<br><br>
                My interests vary from classical music to neorealist cinema, football to minesweeper and from photography to poetry. 
                When not coding, you will almost certainly find me with a book and tea (or, if available, Yirgacheffe coffee) (or sleeping).
                
                
						</h4>
            
       
